HEADWORD: Yellowfish
<hw>Yel"low*fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A rock trout (<spn>Pleurogrammus monopterygius</spn>) found on the
coast of Alaska; -- called also <altname>striped fish</altname>, and
<altname>Atka mackerel</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yellow-golds</ent>⟦br⟧
